targets.query:
from(bucket: "cabot")
  |> range(start: -1m)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "odometry")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "linear")

from(bucket: "cabot")
  |> range(start: -1m)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "odometry")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "angular")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value / 3.141592 * -180.0 }))

from(bucket: "cabot")
  |> range(start: -1m)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "odometry")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "linear")

from(bucket: "cabot")
  |> range(start: -5m)  // Adjust the time range as needed
  |> last()
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "pose_data")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "lat" or r._field == "lng" or r._field == "yaw")
  |> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "lat", "lng", "yaw"])

from(bucket: "cabot")

  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "lat", "lng", "yaw"])

from(bucket: "cabot")
|> range(start: -5m)

  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "lat" or r._field == "lng")

from(bucket: "cabot")
  |> range(start: -1m)  // Adjust the time range as needed
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "pose_data")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "lat" or r._field == "lng" or r._field == "yaw")
  |> pivot(rowKey:["_time"], columnKey: ["_field"], valueColumn: "_value")
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "lat", "lng", "yaw"])
